name: Chewie's AT-ST (V)
Lore: 'Enclosed Chewie''s daring capture of an Imperial AT-ST helped turn the tide in the Battle of Endor.',
Text: 'May add 2 pilots. During battle, if Chewie aboard, may target an opponent''s character or AT-ST present. Draw destiny. Target hit and power = 0 if destiny > defense value. Immune to attrition < 4.',
